Rule.Name: WR - Work Results
Rule.Description:
The Work Results table is not strictly a classification table, but rather a device for linking the other tables as the level of detail is developed through the BIM process. It covers the entire project timeline and includes multi-disciplinary projects (civil engineering, process engineering, architecture and landscape).
'Apply' creates a Classification Reference for selected IFC entity, using Uniclass2-required attributes derived from the item that you choose in the following list.
